metadata.symbol: ICONS FROM THE WORLD, AND NOT
metadata.description: Jeffrey Preston Bezos  né Jorgensen; born January 12, 1964 is an American entrepreneur, media proprietor, investor, computer engineer, and commercial astronaut. He is the founder, executive chairman, and former president and CEO of Amazon. With a net worth of around US$139 billion as of October 2022, Bezos is the third-wealthiest person in the world and was the wealthiest from 2017 to 2021 according to both Bloomberg's Billionaires Index and Forbes.
